extendedInfo.description: Thank you for your interest in the Six "O" Cars Android App.This App allows you to book a Private Hire vehicle from Six "O" Cars.You can:Get a Quotation for your journeyMake a bookingCheck its statusCancel a bookingTrack the vehicle on a mapManage your previous bookingsManage your favourite addressesThe App is intended for U.K. use only, and therefore all addresses are restricted to within the U.K.

reviews.title: Simplicity in itself
reviews.comment: I have been a customer of 60cars for a number of years.  I downloaded this app the other day tried it tonight booked my taxi earlier today using this app.  when the job has been accepted by the driver you are informed and can track the progress which puts you onto google maps in realtime display.  So easy to use can save journeys in set up.  Great job guys guess i wont be talking to you anymore lol Fantastic App
reviews.author: Mark Garside

reviews.title: Good and almost there
reviews.comment: Does not store email or mobile as the back function on phone takes you to previous information page thus removing info previously filed out. Good start though very nice set up well worth it if not just for the pre-booking system
reviews.author: Jamie Hall

reviews.title: Awesome
reviews.comment: I especially like the feature to quickly select the last journey you booked.
reviews.author: Richard Perkins

reviews.title: Perfect
reviews.comment: The Best Way to order a Taxi. 60-60-60 rules:-)
reviews.author: Jakub Broda
